The Public Relations Officer (PRO) of the Nigerian Immigration Service (NIS), Edo State Command, hs been kidnapped.
Bridget Esene was kidnapped in Benin on her way to church o Sunday.
She was ambushed at Iqueniro, off Agbor Road, dragged out of her car and pushed into the kidnappersâ€™ vehicle.
They shot I the air as the vehicles sped off.
The state NIS has officially announced the incident.
As at now, the abductor has demanded no ransom.
Security agencies, especially their top shots have been falling victim of kidnap for ransom since the crime escalated lately in Nigeria.
